<style>
  /* Dark theme styles */
  .long-text-wrapper {
    padding: 150px;
    padding-top: 70px;
    background-color: #1c1c1e;
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  .card {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #3a3a3c;
  }

  .text-card-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3c;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background-color: #3a3a3c;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .sub-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .card-text p,
  .card-text ul {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #d1d1d6;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card-text ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .card-text ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .long-text-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 120px;
  }

  .long-text-nav .nav-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .long-text-nav .nav-pills .nav-link {
    color: #ffffff;
    background-color: #2c2c2e;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3c;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .long-text-nav .nav-pills .nav-link:hover,
  .long-text-nav .nav-pills .nav-link.active {
    background-color: #007bff;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  /* Layout styles */
  .layout {
    display: flex;
  }

  .content {
    width: 80%;
  }

  .navigation {
    width: 20%;
  }
  .navigation ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  /* Responsive design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .layout {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .content,
    .navigation {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .long-text-wrapper {
      padding: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="long-text-wrapper">
  <div class="layout">
    <div class="content">
      <div id="navbar-example2">
        <div class="long-text-items" id="item1">
          <div class="text-card-wrapper">
            <h3 class="sub-title">Our Vision</h3>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-text">
                <p>
                  To create a sustainable and accessible environment for
                  open-source software, fostering innovation, collaboration, and
                  transparency.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="long-text-items" id="item2">
          <div class="text-card-wrapper">
            <h3 class="sub-title">Core Values</h3>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-text">
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Openness</strong>: We believe in the power of
                    open-source software to drive innovation and foster
                    collaboration among developers worldwide.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Community</strong>: Our strength lies in the
                    diversity and inclusivity of our developer community, where
                    everyone's contributions are valued and celebrated.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Transparency</strong>: We are committed to
                    transparency in our processes, decisions, and interactions,
                    ensuring trust and accountability within our community.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="long-text-items" id="item3">
          <div class="text-card-wrapper">
            <h3 class="sub-title">Key Activities</h3>
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="card-text">
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Identification and Forking</strong>: We identify
                    widely-used open-source libraries and packages at risk of
                    becoming closed-source. We create forks of these projects to
                    ensure their continued availability and openness.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>DevOps Infrastructure</strong>: We build robust
                    DevOps infrastructure to streamline development, testing,
                    and deployment processes for the forked projects.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Brand Removal and Integration Cleanup</strong>: We
                    remove for-profit branding and any integration-related code
                    that hinders openness and accessibility.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Multi-Channel Deployment</strong>: We deploy the
                    forked packages on various delivery channels such as npm,
                    Docker, apt, and brew, making them easily accessible to
                    developers across different platforms.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Feature Implementation</strong>: We implement new
                    features and updates to the forked projects with a 1-month
                    Service Level Agreement (SLA), ensuring timely enhancements
                    and bug fixes.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Developer Education</strong>: We educate the
                    developer community about the benefits of using open-source
                    software and making informed choices to support openness and
                    innovation.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Community Forum</strong>: We maintain a vibrant
                    community forum for discussions, knowledge sharing, and
                    collaboration among developers, fostering a supportive and
                    engaged community.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Inter-Library Compatibility</strong>: We address and
                    resolve inter-library compatibility issues, ensuring
                    seamless integration and interoperability for all projects
                    using our forked packages.
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="navigation">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-light long-text-nav">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills">
          <li>
            <a href="#item1" class="nav-link">Our Vision</a>
          </li>
